Home > Music > Nicki Minaj Is About To Drop Something On Tidal Nicki Minaj Is About To Drop Something On Tidal 4 17 Posted by Trevor Smith , Mar 11, 2017 at 02:57pm Could it be a video for one of her new tracks? 
Nicki Minaj just shared three new songs on Friday, but she has one more surprise for fans this weekend. Taking to Twitter, Minaj revealed that she has "created something super dope" for the platform, which will arrive sometime between now and Monday. Just created smthn super dope for Tidal. Seeing as she already gave us so much music this week, it seems more likely that this release will be a video or interview of some sort. A visual for her "No Frauds" diss track with Lil Wayne and Drake would surely get people talking. If you don't currently have Tidal, this may be the time to subscribe, or at least grab a free trial.
